<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Contact Me Services | Premium Agricultural B2B</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,600;1,400&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Auth_CSS/auth-nav.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet" />

    <style>
      /* --- THEME VARIABLES --- */
      :root {
        --bg-main: #0b0f17;
        --bg-surface: #131a26;
        --bg-light: #f8fafc;
        --text-pure: #ffffff;
        --text-muted: #94a3b8;
        --text-dark: #0f172a;
        --text-dark-muted: #475569;
        --accent: #c29b68;
        --border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        --border-color-dark: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.15);
        --sharp: 0px;
      }

      /* --- GLOBAL RESETS --- */
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
        border-radius: var(--sharp) !important;
      }
      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }
      body {
        background-color: var(--bg-main);
        color: var(--text-pure);
        overflow-x: hidden;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      h1,
      h2,
      h3,
      .brand-logo {
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }
      .serif-italic {
        font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 400;
      }
      img {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }

      /* --- CUSTOM CURSOR --- */
      #custom-cursor {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        border: 2px solid var(--accent);
        position: fixed;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 9999;
        mix-blend-mode: difference;
        transition:
          width 0.2s,
          height 0.2s,
          background-color 0.2s;
      }

      /* --- UTILITIES --- */
      .section-tag {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        color: var(--accent);
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .section-title {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
        color: var(--text-pure);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }
      .section-title.dark-text {
        color: var(--text-dark);
      }

      .btn-premium {
        position: relative;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: var(--bg-main);
        padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
        border: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        overflow: hidden;
        z-index: 1;
        transition:
          transform 0.3s ease,
          box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      }
      .btn-premium::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: var(--text-pure);
        transition: left 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        z-index: -1;
      }
      .btn-premium:hover::before {
        left: 0;
      }
      .btn-premium:hover {
        color: var(--bg-main);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(194, 155, 104, 0.2);
      }

      .btn-outline {
        background: transparent;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        color: var(--text-pure);
      }
      .btn-outline::before {
        background: var(--text-pure);
      }
      .btn-outline:hover {
        color: var(--bg-main) !important;
        border-color: var(--text-pure);
      }

      /* --- HEADER --- */
      header {
        background: rgba(11, 15, 23, 0.85);
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        position: fixed;
        width: 100%;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 1000;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      header.scrolled {
        padding: 0.25rem 0;
        background: rgba(11, 15, 23, 0.98);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
      }
      .nav-container {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
        transition: padding 0.3s ease;
      }
      .brand-logo {
        font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.4rem);
        color: var(--text-pure);
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .brand-logo span {
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      nav ul {
        display: flex;
        list-style: none;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: center;
      }
      nav ul li a {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        position: relative;
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
      }
      nav ul li a::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background-color: var(--accent);
        transition: width 0.3s ease;
      }
      nav ul li a:hover::after,
      nav ul li a.active::after {
        width: 100%;
      }
      nav ul li a:hover,
      nav ul li a.active {
        color: var(--text-pure);
      }

      .header-actions {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .btn-header-login {
        padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .mobile-menu-btn {
        display: none;
        color: var(--text-pure);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        background: none;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.5rem;
      }

      /* --- HERO --- */
      .hero {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background:
          linear-gradient(rgba(11, 15, 23, 0.85), rgba(11, 15, 23, 0.98)),
          url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500937386664-56d1dfef3854?q=80&w=2070")
            center/cover no-repeat;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 6rem 2rem 2rem;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .hero-content {
        max-width: 850px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      .hero p {
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        max-width: 650px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }
      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .glow-orb {
        position: absolute;
        width: 50vw;
        height: 50vw;
        max-width: 400px;
        max-height: 400px;
        background: radial-gradient(
          circle,
          rgba(194, 155, 104, 0.08) 0%,
          rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 70%
        );
        top: 20%;
        left: 10%;
        pointer-events: none;
        animation: floatingGlow 8s infinite alternate;
      }
      @keyframes floatingGlow {
        0% {
          transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateY(-40px) scale(1.1);
        }
      }

      /* --- ABOUT --- */
      .about-section {
        background-color: var(--bg-light);
        padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 10rem) 2rem;
      }
      .about-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5rem);
        align-items: center;
      }
      .about-text {
        color: var(--text-dark);
      }
      .about-text p {
        color: var(--text-dark-muted);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2vw, 1.05rem);
      }
      .about-image-wrapper {
        position: relative;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color-dark);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: #ffffff;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .about-image-wrapper img {
        width: 100%;
        display: block;
        transition: transform 0.6s ease;
      }
      .about-image-wrapper:hover img {
        transform: scale(1.03);
      }

      /* --- PRODUCTS --- */
      .products-section {
        padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 10rem) 2rem;
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .grid-3 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 320px), 1fr));
        gap: 2.5rem;
      }
      .product-card {
        background: var(--bg-surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
      }
      .product-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--accent);
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      }
      .product-img-box {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        height: 280px;
      }
      .product-img-box img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: transform 0.6s ease;
      }
      .product-card:hover .product-img-box img {
        transform: scale(1.08);
      }
      .product-badge {
        position: absolute;
        top: 1rem;
        right: 1rem;
        background: rgba(11, 15, 23, 0.9);
        backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border: 1px solid var(--accent);
        z-index: 2;
      }
      .product-info {
        padding: 2rem;
        flex-grow: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      .product-info h3 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .specs-list {
        list-style: none;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .specs-list li {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        padding: 0.6rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }
      .specs-list li strong {
        color: var(--text-pure);
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      /* --- SERVICES --- */
      .services-section {
        background-color: #0e141f;
        padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 10rem) 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      }
      .services-container {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .service-card {
        background: var(--bg-main);
        border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
        padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .service-card:hover {
        background: var(--bg-surface);
        border-left-color: var(--text-pure);
        transform: translateX(5px);
      }
      .service-icon {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      /* --- TEAM --- */
      .team-section {
        padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 10rem) 2rem;
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .team-card {
        background: var(--bg-surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .team-img-box {
        height: 350px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .team-img-box img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        filter: grayscale(100%);
        transition: all 0.5s ease;
      }
      .team-card:hover .team-img-box img {
        filter: grayscale(0%);
        transform: scale(1.04);
      }
      .team-details {
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .team-role {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        display: block;
      }

      /* --- CONTACT --- */
      .contact-section {
        background: var(--bg-light);
        color: var(--text-dark);
        padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 10rem) 2rem;
      }
      .contact-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
        gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem);
      }
      .info-block {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .info-icon {
        width: 55px;
        height: 55px;
        background: var(--text-dark);
        color: #ffffff;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
      .contact-form {
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color-dark);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        width: 100%;
      }
      .form-group {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      .form-group label {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        color: var(--text-dark);
      }
      .form-control {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1rem;
        border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
        background: #f8fafc;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .form-control:focus {
        outline: none;
        border-color: var(--accent);
        background: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(194, 155, 104, 0.1);
      }
      .contact-form .btn-premium {
        width: 100%;
        background: var(--text-dark);
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      /* --- FOOTER --- */
      footer {
        background: #06090e;
        padding: 5rem 2rem 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      }
      .footer-grid {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        padding-bottom: 3rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      }
      .social-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
      }
      .social-links a {
        width: 45px;
        height: 45px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .social-links a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
        border-color: var(--accent);
        transform: translateY(-3px);
      }
      .footer-links ul {
        list-style: none;
      }
      .footer-links ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      }
      .footer-links ul li a {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .footer-links ul li a:hover {
        color: var(--text-pure);
        padding-left: 5px;
      }
      .footer-bottom {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--text-dark-muted);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      /* --- FULL RESPONSIVE MEDIA QUERIES --- */
      @media (max-width: 992px) {
        .about-container,
        .contact-container,
        .footer-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 3rem;
        }
        #custom-cursor {
          display: none !important;
        }

        /* Mobile Navbar Details */
        .mobile-menu-btn {
          display: block;
        }
        nav {
          position: absolute;
          top: 100%;
          left: 0;
          width: 100%;
          background: rgba(19, 26, 38, 0.98);
          backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
          border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
          transform: translateY(-150%);
          opacity: 0;
          visibility: hidden;
          transition: all 0.4s ease;
          z-index: 999;
          box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        nav.active {
          transform: translateY(0);
          opacity: 1;
          visibility: visible;
        }
        nav ul {
          flex-direction: column;
          padding: 2rem;
          gap: 1.5rem;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .nav-container {
          padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        }
        .hero-actions {
          flex-direction: column;
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 350px;
          margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .hero-actions .btn-premium {
          width: 100%;
        }
        .footer-bottom {
          flex-direction: column;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .grid-3 {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        } /* Stack perfectly on very small phones */
        .product-img-box,
        .team-img-box {
          height: 250px;
        }
        .contact-form {
          padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        .about-image-wrapper {
          padding: 0.75rem;
        }
        .header-actions .btn-header-login {
          display: none; /* Hide login in header for ultra-small screens, maybe put in mobile menu */
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="custom-cursor"></div>

    <header id="main-header">
      <div class="nav-container">
        <a href="#" class="brand-logo">Contact Me <span>Services</span></a>

        <nav id="navbar">
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/api/v1/home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="active">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#products">Products</a></li>
            <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#team">Our Team</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            <% if (authUser) { %>
            <li class="mobile-login auth-mobile-item" style="display: none">
              <a href="/api/v1/profile" style="color: var(--accent)">
                Profile
              </a>
            </li>
            <% } else { %>
            <li class="mobile-login auth-mobile-item" style="display: none">
              <a href="/api/v1/login?returnTo=%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fb1" style="color: var(--accent)">
                Login Portal
              </a>
            </li>
            <% } %>
          </ul>
        </nav>

        <div class="header-actions">
          <% if (authUser) { %>
          <%- include('../partials/authActions') %>
          <% } else { %>
          <button class="btn-premium btn-header-login" id="apiLoginBtn">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-right-to-bracket"></i> Login
          </button>
          <% } %>
          <button class="mobile-menu-btn" id="mobileMenuToggle">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="glow-orb"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="section-tag" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="1000"
          >Premium Agriculture B2B Engine</span
        >
        <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1200" data-aos-delay="200">
          Premium Farm Ready<br /><span class="serif-italic"
            >Agriculture Products</span
          >
        </h1>
        <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1200" data-aos-delay="400">
          From farm to table, we deliver the highest quality dehydrated powders
          and custom agricultural solutions for health, medicine, and culinary
          applications.
        </p>
        <div
          class="hero-actions"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-duration="1200"
          data-aos-delay="600"
        >
          <a href="#products" class="btn-premium"
            >Our Products <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i
          ></a>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-premium btn-outline">Get In Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about-text" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1000">
          <span class="section-tag">Since 2022</span>
          <h2 class="section-title dark-text">About Contact Me Services</h2>
          <p>
            Welcome to Contact Me Services, a visionary venture founded in 2022
            by Anand Jain, dedicated to redefining daily nutrition. We believe
            that the vibrant essence of sun-ripened fruits and garden-fresh
            vegetables should be accessible in its most potent and pristine
            form.
          </p>
          <p>
            Through a gentle, state-of-the-art dehydration process, we carefully
            preserve the vital nutrients, vibrant colors, and intense flavors of
            nature's bounty.
          </p>
          <a
            href="#contact"
            class="btn-premium"
            style="background: var(--text-dark); color: white"
            >Get Started</a
          >
        </div>
        <div
          class="about-image-wrapper"
          data-aos="fade-left"
          data-aos-duration="1000"
        >
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500937386664-56d1dfef3854?q=80&w=600"
            alt="Agricultural Fields"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="products-section" id="products">
      <span class="section-tag" data-aos="fade-up">B2B Portfolio</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        Our Premium Products
      </h2>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="product-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000">
          <div class="product-img-box">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615485290382-441e4d049cb5?q=80&w=500"
              alt="Onion Powder"
